Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.15,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Eba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:56.40,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Ah, mas se você ficar boa na cozinha, nossa balança irá...
